#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.9:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Dhanavagga "
msgstr "1. Wealth "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 9. Pahānasutta → saññojanappahānasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Pahānasutta "
msgstr "9. Giving Up "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.8, sc1
msgctxt "an7.9:1.1"
msgid "“Sattannaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃyojanānaṃ pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the spiritual life is lived to give up and cut out these seven fetters. "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.3"
msgid "Anunayasaṃyojanassa pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati, paṭighasaṃyojanassa … pe … "
msgstr "The fetters of attraction, repulsion, views, doubt, conceit, desire to be reborn, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.4"
msgid "diṭṭhisaṃyojanassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.5"
msgid "vicikicchāsaṃyojanassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.6"
msgid "mānasaṃyojanassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.7"
msgid "bhavarāgasaṃyojanassa … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.8"
msgid "avijjāsaṃyojanassa pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.9"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sattannaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ pahānāya samucchedāya brahmacariyaṃ vussati. "
msgstr "The spiritual life is lived to give up and cut out these seven fetters. "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.10"
msgid "Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno anunayasaṃyojanaṃ pahīnaṃ hoti ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ. "
msgstr "When a mendicant has given up the fetters of attraction, repulsion, views, doubt, conceit, desire to be reborn, and ignorance—cut them off at the root, made them like a palm stump, obliterated them, so they are unable to arise in the future—"

msgctxt "an7.9:1.11"
msgid "Paṭighasaṃyojanaṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.12"
msgid "diṭṭhisaṃyojanaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.13"
msgid "vicikicchāsaṃyojanaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.14"
msgid "mānasaṃyojanaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.15"
msgid "bhavarāgasaṃyojanaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.16"
msgid "avijjāsaṃyojanaṃ pahīnaṃ hoti ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhammaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.9:1.17"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhikkhu acchecchi taṇhaṃ, vivattayi saṃyojanaṃ, sammā mānābhisamayā antamakāsi dukkhassā”ti. "
msgstr "they’re called a mendicant who has cut off craving, untied the fetters, and by rightly comprehending conceit has made an end of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.9:1.18"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
